兴味索然，安全渡亡为其唯一专念。_#','#_雅睿歐斯對諸神與凡人間的爭鬥興味索然，安全渡亡為其唯一專念。_#','#_Athréos ne se préoccupe pas du conflit opposant les autres dieux aux mortels. Tout ce qui l''intéresse, c''est d''assurer le passage des morts._#','#_Athreos bedeuten die Konflikte anderer Götter mit den Sterblichen wenig. Er kümmert sich einzig um die sichere Überfahrt der Toten._#','#_Atreo non ha interesse per i conflitti degli altri dei con i mortali. Si cura solo di garantire un passaggio sicuro ai morti._#','#_エイスリオスは他の神々と定命の者たちとの戦いにさしたる興味は無かった。彼の唯一の関心は、死者の無事な通過だけにあった。_#','#_Atreos não se importa com os conflitos dos outros deuses com os mortais. Sua única preocupação é garantir uma passagem segura aos mortos._#','#_Атрею нет дела до борьбы богов и смертных. Его заботит лишь безопасность пути для павших._#','#_A Atreos le importa poco el conflicto de los demás dioses con los mortales. Solo le preocupa que los muertos tengan una travesía segura._#','#_에스리오스는 필멸자와 다른 신들의 싸움에는 별 관심이 없다. 오직 죽은 자들의 안전한 여행만이 그의 관심사이다._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('380365','Aerial Formation','JOU','Instant','C','{U}','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Strive — This spell costs {2}{U} more to cast for each target beyond the first.£Any number of target creatures each get +1/+1 and gain flying until end of turn.',NULL,NULL,'Zack Stella','30','2.583','£4/26/2014: You choose how many targets each spell with a strive ability has and what those targets are as you cast it. It’s legal to cast such a spell with no targets, although this is rarely a good idea. You can’t choose the same target more than once for a single strive spell.£4/26/2014: The mana cost and converted mana cost of strive spells don’t change no matter how many targets they have. Strive abilities affect only what you pay.£4/26/2014: If all of the spell’s targets are illegal when the spell tries to resolve, it won’t resolve and none of its effects will happen. If one or more of its targets are legal when it tries to resolve, the spell will resolv